ZH: 大家一起开动吧！
EN: Let's all start eating together!

ZH: 开动前先洗手。
EN: Wash your hands before you start eating.

ZH: 请您恕我先开动。
EN: Please excuse me for starting first.

ZH: 开动之前要祈祷。
EN: Say a prayer before you start eating.

ZH: 开动时要记住说谢谢。
EN: Remember to say thank you when you start eating.

ZH: 开动之后我们可以开始聊天。
EN: We can start chatting after we start eating.

ZH: 你们都准备好了吗？我们要开始开动了。
EN: Are you all ready? We are about to start eating.

ZH: 开动后，大家可以随意取用。
EN: After starting, everyone can help themselves.

ZH: 老人家请先开动。
EN: Please let the elder start eating first.

ZH: 开动之际，不要用手抓食物。
EN: Do not use your hands to grab food when starting.

ZH: 你说的让我们都忍不住要开动了！
EN: What you said made us all eager to start eating!

ZH: 开动之前可以稍微休息一下。
EN: You can take a short break before starting to eat.

ZH: 开动时不要吹灭蜡烛。
EN: Do not blow out the candles when you start eating.

ZH: 开动前请先等我一下。
EN: Please wait for me before you start eating.

ZH: 开动之后我们可以讨论新计划。
EN: We can discuss the new plan after we start eating.

ZH: 开动前先回答一个问题。
EN: Answer a question before you start eating.

ZH: 开动时别忘了递盘子给旁边的人。
EN: Don't forget to pass the plate to the person next to you when starting.

ZH: 一起开动吧，我等不及要吃了！
EN: Let's start eating together, I can't wait to eat!

ZH: 开动之前先做个小游戏吧。
EN: Let's play a small game before starting to eat.

ZH: 饭菜都准备好了，我们开始开动吧！
EN: The food is ready, let's start eating!
